Here are all 4 liboqs build commands:

## x86-64 — WITH AVX2 (SIMD)
```bash
rm -rf liboqs/build_x86_64_simd
cmake -S liboqs -B liboqs/build_x86_64_simd -GNinja \
      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release \
      -DOQS_BUILD_ONLY_LIB=ON \
      -DOQS_DIST_BUILD=OFF \
      -DOQS_ENABLE_KEM_ml_kem_768=ON \
      -DOQS_ENABLE_SIG_ml_dsa_65=ON \
      -DOQS_USE_AVX2_INSTRUCTIONS=ON \
      -DOQS_USE_BMI2_INSTRUCTIONS=ON \
      -DOQS_USE_POPCNT_INSTRUCTIONS=ON \
      -DCMAKE_C_FLAGS="-march=native -O3" \
      -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=OFF
cmake --build liboqs/build_x86_64_simd -j$(nproc)
```

