**Key flag differences at a glance:**

| Flag | SIMD | No SIMD |
|---|---|---|
| `OQS_DIST_BUILD` | `OFF` | `ON` |
| `OQS_USE_AVX2_INSTRUCTIONS` / `OQS_USE_ARM_NEON_INSTRUCTIONS` | `ON` | `OFF` |
| `CMAKE_C_FLAGS` | `-march=native -O3` | `-O3` only |

Run `rm -rf` on the build folder first every time — otherwise CMake throws the stale cache error you saw earlier.